{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, one had to sit down first and the other one sat in your-- close to your body.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to spread your legs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is the way we were packed in there because for the lack of space in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was a very uncomfortable way to sit for two days like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't get up and it was just terrible, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you couldn't go to the latrines or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, we were allowed to come out of this barrack, and we were given our striped outfits.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken to a camp called Melk, which was also further west of Mauthausen on the Danube River.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in this old barrack that was used by cavalry in the Austro-Hungarian-- in the first World War, I think.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was on top of a hill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On one side, we could see this huge monastery, which is very famous-- the Melk monastery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And below us was the railroad station and the Danube River.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was put into a detail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were many Russian prisoners of war, as well as prisoners here, who did not get any other treatment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They received the same treatment as we did, even though they were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was working on a detail where we were taken, every day, on a train, well, in boxcars, with two SS men inside, in the middle of the boxcar, through a tunnel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we worked in a big place that had-- they were digging six shafts into the mountain.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
